                  <p class="profile_intro">In 1962, Samoa became the first country 
                    in the Pacific to gain independence. The Faa Samoa (the Samoan 
                    way) continues to rule the everyday life of the population. 
                  <p align="center"><img src="../../img/maps/cp_samoa.gif" width="480" height="253" alt="Map of Samoa"> 
                  </p>
                  <h5><a name="facts"></a>Facts and Figures</h5>
